                <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6">Steps to follow:</h2>
                <ol class="list-decimal pl-6">
                    <li>Appear for the entrance test.</li>
                    <li>Qualify the test with at least 40%.</li>
                    <li>Attend the personal interview.</li>
                    <li>GATE qualification contributes to final scoring.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
         </div>
        </div>
      </div>
